import Vue from 'vue'
import './plugins/axios'
import App from './App.vue'
import router from './router'
import store from './store'
import ElementUI from 'element-ui'
import './styles.scss'
import '@/assets/css/main.css'
Vue.use(ElementUI)

Vue.config.productionTip = false

new Vue({
  router,
  store,
  render: h => h(App),
}).$mount('#app')
